comments: Monk (LAL) extends his hand forward and makes contact to Lowry's (MIA) front that affects his his shot near the rim.
Tucker (MIA) swipes down and makes contact to Davis' (LAL) head/face as he secures possession of the rebound.
Anthony (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Robinson (MIA)  and absorbs the contact.
Robinson (MIA) makes contact with Monk's (LAL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Monk (LAL) makes marginal contact to Robinson's (MIA) lower body as he receives the pass and jumps in the air. The contact does not affect his ability to make the pass.
After the pump fake Adebayo (MIA) leans in and makes marginal contact with Davis' (LAL) body, Davis' reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Westbrook (LAL) Firms up and absorbs the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to Davis' (LAL) arm that affects his putback shot attempt.
Monk (LAL) makes marginal contact with Tucker (MIA) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Anthony (LAL) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Tucker (MIA) continues to move forward and initiates contact to Westbrook's (LAL) side that affects his SQBR and ability to pass at the end of the drive.
Bradley (LAL) makes incidental hand to hand contact to Robinson's (MIA) off hand following the release of his shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) makes contact with Adebayo's (MIA) arm during his shot near the rim.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to Anthony's (LAL) arm that causes him to lose possession of the ball.
Anthony (LAL) does not make the inbound pass within the five seconds allotted to his team.
Robinson (MIA) commits a take foul on Anthony (LAL).
Westbrook (LAL) clamps and hold Dedmon's (MIA) arm while pursuing the rebound.
